The paper focuses on analyzing security threats and challenges in various edge computing paradigms, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses networking and distributed computing aspects, which are covered by the sub-categories of computer networks (cs.NI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses software engineering and system design aspects, which are covered by the sub-categories of software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY).
